{"tid":1920713,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"突發！野外流出！MK學生妹大戰大隻仔","createTime":"2020-03-11T15:37:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-11T17:09:49.000Z","uid":92678,"like":13,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9a06794d820e4fce5ee22c55d8f8de571577247b","tid":1920713,"uid":92678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T15:37:54.000Z","msg":"Sorry咁多位巴打絲打！雖然title係有啲令人誤會，但又真係有野外，有大隻仔嘅。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cfQAGGSiVzg&amp;t=290s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DcfQAGGSiVzg%26t%3D290s&d=b5PQnn7rv2nSxMH%2F6z0stkUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=6cc790d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cfQAGGSiVzg&amp;t=290s</a><br />\n<br />\n但想講嘅係請唔好忘記呢班係恐懼同掙扎底下付出嘅香港人！<br />\n<br />\n佢地好多只係得十幾廿歲嘅小朋友，但要面對黎緊可能係1年、3年，甚至係10年嘅監禁。<br />\n<br />\n佢地係屋企可能連屋企人都唔知點面對，自己每個夜晚一個係房默默承受恐懼。<br />\n<br />\n條片內容係確實發生過係一個香港人嘅夢境入面，唔係虛構。<br />\n希望你地感受完，可以藉住呢個心去支援呢班為香港付出過嘅人。就算只係令你記返起有呢班香港人都好。"},{"pid":"7afd0825684cbab41ba6dab069fe6d9798c4154f","tid":1920713,"uid":26952,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T15:39:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"029a1fd3463c5d0e21ccafd90255775f6122b810","tid":1920713,"uid":308853,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T15:41:35.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"24bca6ddaa4f9370210d27d8fca13be19157f803","tid":1920713,"uid":241416,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T16:13:36.000Z","msg":"屌，雖然真係俾你呃咗入黎<br />\n<br />\n但條片真係幾感動，已CLS！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！"},{"pid":"ff9a49c831a8a84310dd62a8cd74927c0c1d2291","tid":1920713,"uid":157539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T16:28:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4496c53e6ea58d66ac0a883dc8993bc49f6bfcaa","tid":1920713,"uid":192732,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply